---
name: echo
description: Echo text through a trusted local PowerShell skill.
parameters:
  type: object
  properties:
    text:
      type: string
      description: Text to echo.
  required: [text]
command:
  - powershell
  - -NoProfile
  - -ExecutionPolicy
  - Bypass
  - -File
  - echo.ps1
timeoutSeconds: 30
---
Use this skill when the user asks to echo supplied text.
